window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>In audio for the first time since its 2015 e-book release!</b><br> <br> A whirlwind of luxury, crime, and sexual thrill was what Isla Maran found overnight with Abram Lenox. But she left it all behind to let him hunt and kill Jesse Toro. She left him for her shot at normal.<br> <br> But there's no chance for that now. Now, in the hands of Jesse Toro, Isla has no choice but to be a part of this—to be caught in the crosshairs of a war that will end in bloodshed only she can stop. Because with Jesse, she discovers shocking lies that will change the whole course of the chase. Lies that will change absolutely everything.<br> <br> Suddenly, armed with the most fatal truths, Isla finds herself facing twice the danger and lust as she is forced to play both sides, torn between two dangerous men plagued by darkness and damage she can only pray to heal.<br> <br> <i>Damage</i> is the second and final part to <i>Havoc</i>.<br> <br> Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
